01:04:30.453 --> 01:04:31.995
<i>Is this really the artist's role?</i>

01:04:32.621 --> 01:04:37.708
NINA: <i>Well, I think it's something</i>
<i>that, um, I have chosen to do</i>

01:04:37.793 --> 01:04:41.420
<i>and I have felt compelled to do it.</i>

01:04:41.505 --> 01:04:43.714
<i>So it is my role...</i>

01:04:43.799 --> 01:04:47.385
<i>but sometimes, I wish it wasn't.</i>

01:04:47.470 --> 01:04:49.387
<i>I think that the artists</i>

01:04:49.472 --> 01:04:53.015
<i>who don't get involved
in preaching messages</i>

01:04:53.100 --> 01:04:55.351
<i>probably are happier,</i>

01:04:55.436 --> 01:05:00.524
<i>but you see, I have to live with Nina,
