01:05:04.862 --> 01:05:09.114
<i># Baby, do you understand me now? #</i>

01:05:09.199 --> 01:05:10.534
[APPLAUSE]

01:05:13.036 --> 01:05:17.791
<i># If sometimes you see that I'm mad #</i>

