somewhere...

01:06:02.545 --> 01:06:04.086
where I didn't feel those pressures.

01:06:04.171 --> 01:06:11.136
<i># Don't let me be misunderstood #</i>

01:06:14.682 --> 01:06:17.350
<i># Cause if I’m misunderstood #</i>

01:06:17.435 --> 01:06:21.188
<i># All my life would have been in vain #</i>

01:06:25.484 --> 01:06:31.489
<i># And Lord knows I don’t want
