01:06:31.574 --> 01:06:33.198
<i># So don't let me be... #</i>

01:06:33.283 --> 01:06:36.577
AL: <i>By the late '60s,</i>
<i>I realized that Nina was fighting</i>

01:06:36.662 --> 01:06:40.038
demons that could appear
