01:06:40.123 --> 01:06:43.166
<i>She could get violent,
she could get really physical,</i>

01:06:43.251 --> 01:06:46.128
<i>and the change in her would be dramatic...</i>

01:06:46.213 --> 01:06:48.422
boom, like a switch.

01:06:48.507 --> 01:06:52.343
