01:07:35.053 --> 01:07:38.556
<i>and they were unable to find anything.</i>

01:07:38.641 --> 01:07:43.311
NINA: [SINGING] <i># Give me a clear mind #</i>

01:07:45.814 --> 01:07:52.780
<i># Give me the words to say what I mean #</i>

01:07:57.075 --> 01:08:03.541
<i># Don’t let me be misunderstood #</i>

01:08:15.553 --> 01:08:19.848
ANDY: <i>And her downward spiral,</i>
