01:08:20.849 --> 01:08:23.475
<i>We did a tour with Bill Cosby,</i>

01:08:23.560 --> 01:08:27.104
<i>and the last night, she became erratic.</i>

01:08:27.189 --> 01:08:29.857
<i>She had a can of shoe polish.</i>

01:08:29.942 --> 01:08:32.274
<i>She was putting it in her hair.</i>

01:08:32.359 --> 01:08:35.278
<i>And she began talking gibberish,</i>

