01:09:36.549 --> 01:09:37.550
INTERVIEWER: <i>Right.</i>

01:09:37.635 --> 01:09:40.761
NINA: <i>He didn't know how to touch me</i>
<i>and he never had enough time.</i>

01:09:40.845 --> 01:09:45.225
<i>He'd come to see me late at night
