01:10:22.345 --> 01:10:26.558
<i>People sacrificed sanity,
well-being, life.</i>

01:10:27.475 --> 01:10:29.935
<i>Nina Simone was a free spirit</i>

01:10:30.020 --> 01:10:33.939
<i>in an era that didn't really
appreciate a woman's genius.</i>

01:10:34.024 --> 01:10:38.401
<i>So what does that do
